{"id":233004676,"title":"#口罩 簡單的數學問題","content":"https://i.imgur.com/j7vYf9e.jpg\n台灣人口2千多萬  產能每天1千萬\n請問怎麼讓每個人每天都有口罩戴？\n\n當然不夠啊  怎麼分都不夠\n就算真的實名制分發  1千萬分給2千多萬？\n唯一的解法就是每人一次買3片  每次間隔至少7天\n可能有人有問題：一個口罩怎麼戴兩天\n所以要配套宣導：減少出門次數，能不出門就不出門；甚至與外送平台配合  減少外送運費\n\n若還是不夠就是再延長間隔\n若考慮到醫護人員一天一個   間隔一樣要再延長\n或許可以考慮對民眾宣導口罩噴酒精能用兩天","excerpt":"台灣人口2千多萬  產能每天1千萬，請問怎麼讓每個人每天都有口罩戴？當然不夠啊  怎麼分都不夠，就算真的實名制分發  1千萬分給2千多萬？唯一的解法就是每人一次買3片  每次間隔至少7天，可能有人有問","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"fc7574ad-e1df-43d2-bb06-8825c718c065","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-02-02T17:58:35.131Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-02T18:00:20.134Z","commentCount":7,"likeCount":27,"tags":[],"topics":["口罩"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"時事","forumAlias":"trending","school":"國立虎尾科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":23},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":4}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/j7vYf9e.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"be477304-4859-4d79-9dec-4c298083c90a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/j7vYf9el.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/j7vYf9el.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/j7vYf9el.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-02-02T17:58:35.131Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-02T18:00:20.134Z"},{"id":"be477304-4859-4d79-9dec-4c298083c90a","url":"https://i.imgur.com/j7vYf9e.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/j7vYf9e","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/j7vYf9el.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-02-02T17:58:35.131Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-02T18:00:20.134Z"}],"postAvatar":""}